verse:
5 The Lord, the Lord Almighty—
he touches the earth and it melts, and all who live in it mourn;
the whole land rises like the Nile, then sinks like the river of Egypt; 6 he builds his lofty palace[a] in the heavens and sets its foundation[b] on the earth;
he calls for the waters of the sea and pours them out over the face of the land— the Lord is his name.
